prompts.frontCover:
Flat 2D watercolor painting of a humorous birthday card front. The scene features cartoon-illustrated versions of Lao Lao and Jordan from the reference photo, set against a simple, light-wash watercolor background.

Lao Lao, an East Asian woman with long, straight dark brown hair and thin, gold-rimmed glasses, is in the foreground. She's wearing a light blue crewneck sweatshirt and has a comically exaggerated expression of mock-annoyance or playful struggle.

Behind her, Jordan, an East Asian man with short, dark, textured hair, is giving her a giant bear hug. He is wearing a tan hoodie and has a huge, beaming, cheerful grin on his face, clearly delighted. The hug is so enthusiastic that it's slightly squishing Lao Lao, creating a funny, lighthearted scene that looks like he's joyfully overwhelming her with affection. Their clothing (omitting logos) and physical appearances highly resemble the people in the photo.

The entire illustration is done in a soft, flowing watercolor style with visible paper texture, artistic brush strokes, and soft color bleeds, giving it a beautiful and charming feel.

Centered in a clear space above the couple, the text "Happy Birthday to my favorite person to annoy" is written in a beautiful, readable, elegant handwritten cursive script.

- Reference photos provided for character creation
- Characters should only appear on the front cover
- Transform real people into artistic cartoon/illustrated versions matching the style
- Maintain recognizable features while adapting to the artistic style
